'''crease'''
#A [[line]] or [[mark]] made by [[fold]]ing or [[double|doubling]] any [[pliable]] [[substance]]; hence, a similar mark, however produced.
#{{cricket}} One of the [[white]] [[line]]s drawn on the [[pitch]] to show different [[area]]s of [[play]]; especially the [[popping crease]], but also the [[bowling crease]] and the [[return crease]].

